Paper: hep-th/0302161

Date: 2003-02-20

Title: A note and a new perspective on particle horizon problem

Authors: Zhang Hongsheng

Comments: 16 pages, 3 figures

We cautiously reanalyze some easyly confused notions on particle horizonproblem in this paper and then we give a new answer to the particle horizonproblem. This answer is independent of physics plunging into Planck time.